            <div class="rp-raceCourse__row ui-accordion__header
                                                                                                " data-ng-class="{ 'ui-accordion__header_active': isPaneSelected(297)}" id="297" data-ng-click="selectPane(297)" data-ng-init="                                    collapsePane(297)                                " data-test-selector="link-arrowArea">
                <img src="https://www.rp-assets.com/pdfs/RP1-136x48-aus.jpg" class="rp-raceCourse__row__image" alt="Flemington Racecourse" data-test-selector="img-courseImg">                <h2 class="rp-raceCourse__row__name" data-test-selector="course-name" data-test-view="list-results">
